text: Lindome is a locality in Mölndal Municipality in Västra Götaland County in Sweden. In 2010, 13,830 people lived there (11,037 inhabitants in the locality in 2010). Swedish comic creator Rune Andreasson was born there in 1925. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Settlements in Vastra Gotaland County
